                <h3 class="h5">Pre-diabetes gets its due: New $1.2 million award aimed at early intervention and treatment</h3>
            </a>
            <p>Carolina Solis-Herrera, MD, a physician-scientist, associate professor and chief of endocrinology at The University of Texas Health Science Center at San Antonio (UT Health San Antonio) has received a first-of-its-kind, $1.2 million award from Baptist Health Foundation of San Antonio to implement early intervention measures for the condition. </p>
            
        </div>
        <div class="cell large-3 medium-6 small-12">
